cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.HC, cs.SI, cs.MM

The paper deals with bot detection, which is a security and privacy-related topic, suggesting that it belongs to the cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) category. The paper also uses machine learning techniques to classify sensor data, indicating that it could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper focuses on mobile devices, which suggests that it could be classified under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The paper also mentions the use of sensor data, which could be classified under cs.SI (Signal Processing). Finally, the paper implements a proof of concept as an Android service, which could be classified under cs.MM (Multimedia).
